<p class="ayah 88-13" id="13" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Therein</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سُرُرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) thrones</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّرْفُوعَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">raised high,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>13<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-14" id="14" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَكْوَابٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And cups</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّوْضُوعَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">put in place,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>14<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-15" id="15" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنَمَارِقُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And cushions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَصْفُوفَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">lined up,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>15<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-16" id="16" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَزَرَابِىُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And carpets</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَبْثُوثَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">spread out.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>16<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
