<p class="ayah 88-19" id="19" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And at</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجِبَالِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the mountains,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَيْفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">how</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُصِبَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they are fixed?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>19<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-20" id="20" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And at</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَيْفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">how</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سُطِحَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it is spread out?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>20<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-21" id="21" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَذَكِّرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So remind,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُذَكِّرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) a reminder.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>21<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-22" id="22" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّسْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You are not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمُصَيْطِرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a controller,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>22<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-23" id="23" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَوَلَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">turns away</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَفَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and disbelieves,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>23<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-24" id="24" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then Allah will punish him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَذَابَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(with) the punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَكْبَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">greatest.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-25" id="25" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِيَابَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) their return,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>25<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 88-26" id="26" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon Us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حِسَابَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) their account.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>26<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
